                        <interp inst="t18410405-name-124" type="given" value="SARAH"></interp>SARAH HENDERSON</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I was robbed on a Wednesday. (—Brough, of the Ram Inn, Smithfield; Mary Cooper, of Black</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184104050021"></xptr>
               <p>Horse-court, Horse-course, Aldersgate-street; and William Jervis, upholsterer, in Old Kent-road, gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
